<p><a href='/thvote/2014'>&lt;= 2014</a> <a href='/thvote/2011'>2011 =&gt;</a></p>
<p>An English translation of the full results of the 2012 incarnation of the annual THWiki Popularity Poll, held from 19 February 2012 to 25 February 2012.</p>
<p>The poll was not held in 2013 due to a lack of a new main series game and its content, despite the fact that in the future, in years without a new game, the poll would still be held.</p>
<p>All of the table columns are sortable.</p>
<p>Source: <a href='http://toho-vote.info/'>http://toho-vote.info/</a></p>
